
===================
== Documentation ==
===================

The report / documentation is in the docs directory and is named "problem4.pdf".


===============
== Compiling ==
===============

Open a command prompt and type:

make

This will generate three executables in the bin directory.


===============
== Running   ==
===============

Open a command prompt and type:

bin/gen_unsorted_list

This will generate a file named "unsorted_list" with a unsorted array of integer values.


To run the serial code type:

bin/sort_serial

The code will generated a sorted output file named "serial_sorted_list".


To run the parallel code type:

mpirun -np 10 bin/sort_parallel

The code will generated a sorted output file named "parallel_sorted_list".
